You can also verify OUR signature thru your terminal (ssh and curl cmd) via our api:

plain command:
echo "" | curl -F 'signature=<-' https://verify.newznzb.info

sample good signature command:
echo "('-----BEGIN newzNZB SIGNATURE-----', '', '<1484294126.33222.42@PRiVATE>', '-----END newzNZB SIGNATURE-----')" | curl -F 'signature=<-' https://verify.newznzb.info

